title: Steve of Minecraftia
description: The first episode in a new Minecraft machinima series. Set hundreds of years after Minecraftian, this series tells the story of a 'new' Steve and his adventures in Minecraftia. The story has lots of twists and turns, it ties in a lot with Minecraftian and could be considered a sequel. This episode is shorter than future episodes will be since I want to hear feedback before continuing. Also, this episode was just to introduce the legend of the Minecraftian which will be my next upload enjoy all.
